Description: PALMmbQTL provides a scalable Poisson mixed-model framework for
    microbiome QTL (mbQTL) mapping. The method fits a feature-shared
    random-intercept Poisson mixed model to account for compositional
    correlation among taxa and computes genome-wide score statistics
    efficiently by fitting the null model only once. The package implements
    null model fitting and score statistic computation for large-scale
    mbQTL analysis.
